"Execute HTTP operation <small>(GET, POST, PUT, or PATCH request "
"methods)</small> to a URL, (optionally) including the webform "
"submissions."
msgstr ""
"Utför en HTTP-operation <small>(GET, POST, PUT eller PATCH "
"request-metoder)</small> till en URL, (valfritt) inklusive "
"webformulärinlämningar."

